      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_strength_past7days_foot_ankle_opt_1": "No strength at all",
      "memory_820701": "These questions are about your memory and thinking.",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_things": "2a.  In the past week, how difficult was it for you to remember things that people just told you?",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_things_opt_5": "Not difficult at all",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_things_opt_4": "A little difficult",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_things_opt_3": "Somewhat difficult",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_things_opt_2": "Very difficult",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_things_opt_1": "Extremely difficult",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_previousday": "2b.  In the past week, how difficult was it for you to remember things that happened the day before?",
