      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_previousday_opt_1": "Extremely difficult",
      "functionalityafterstrokeadult_difficult_past7days_remember_dothings": "2c.  In the past week, how difficult was it for you to remember to do things (e.g., keep scheduled appointments or take medication)?",
